item.title: 【Live Audios (lossless)】WAV - Madonna - The Celebration Tour In Rio (Rebroadcast) (WAV and M4A) 2024
item.description:
Credits: @Yatama_Lima (Twitter)

Improved audio and normalized volume levels using Logic Pro

01. It's a Celebration (with Bob the Drag Queen) (Bob the Drag Queen; "D&D", "Lucky Star", "Celebration", "Erotica", "Vogue", "BIM" & "Material Girl")
02. Nothing Really Matters (contains elements from the Club 69 Remix)
03. Everybody (contains elements of "Where's the Party")
04. Into the Groove (contains elements of "Into the Hollywood Groove")
05. Speech #1
06. Burning Up
07. Open Your Heart
08. Holiday (contains elements of "I Want Your Love" by Chic)
09. The Storm (contains elements of "In This Life")
09. Live to Tell
10. The Ritual (Dancers interlude; contains elements of "Girl Gone Wild")
10. Like a Prayer (contains elements of "Birjina Gaztetto Bat Zegoen", "Unholy", "Girl Gone Wild" & "Act of Contrition")
11. Living for Love (contains elements of the Offer Nissim Remix, Prince’s “Let’s Go Crazy” & Eddie Copley’s “Fever”)
12. The 90s (Interlude)
13. Erotica (contains elements of "Justify My Love", "You Thrill Me" & "Papa Don't Preach")
14. Justify My Love (contains elements of Kehlani's "Gangsta", Peggy Lee's “Fever” & "Erotica")
15. Fever
16. Hung Up (contains elements of Hung Up on Tokischa)
17. Bad Girl (contains elements of Charles Mayer’s “Le Regret, op. 332", Mercy James on piano)
18. Ballroom (dancers interlude; contains elements of "Up Down Suite", "Vogue" & BREAK MY SOUL (THE QUEENS REMIX))
18. Vogue (with Anitta)
19. Human Nature (Shortened)
20. Crazy for You (Shortened)
21. The Beast Within (contains elements of "Justify My Love")
22. Die Another Day
23. Don't Tell Me (contains elements of "The Good, the Bad & the Ugly")
24. Speech #2
25. This Little Light of Mine (Acapella)
26. Express Yourself (Acoustic; extended outro)
27. La Isla Bonita
28. Music (with Pabllo Vittar) (Also with young musicians from Rio different samba schools - Tour debut. Samba version)
29. Madonna (video interlude; contains elements of "I Don't Search I Find")
30. Bedtime Story (contains elements of the Sound Factory Remix)
31. Ray of Light (Sasha Ultra Violet Remix)
32. Rain
33. Billie Jean / Like a Virgin (contains elements of Express Yourself, Angel & Smooth Criminal, Dangerous, YRMW, TWYMMF by MJ)
34. Bitch I'm Madonna (contains elements of "Give Me All Your Luvin")
35. Celebration (shortened instrumental outro; contains elements of “Music”; Benny Benassi Remix.)
35. The Power of Good-Bye
35. Isn't It a Pity (George Harrison song)
